headline: What Catalysts Are Shaping the Changing Story for Cadence Bank
summary: Cadence Bank’s consensus analyst price target has risen modestly to $42.70, up from a previous estimate of $42.27. This uptick comes as market sentiment shifts in response to the recently announced merger with Huntington Bancshares, which has sparked increased optimism about the strategic fit and growth potential of the combined entity. Stay tuned to learn how you can stay ahead of the latest updates as analysts continue to reassess Cadence Bank’s outlook in the evolving landscape. Analyst...
